		<div id="collapse-TCPV-Eight" class="collapse" aria-labelledby="heading-TCPV-Eight" data-parent="#accordion-TCPV">
			<div class="card-body">
				<p>By using this site, you consent to the collection and use of this information by Dream Dinners&reg;. If we decide to change our privacy policy, we will post those changes on this page so that you are always aware of what information we collect, how we use it, and under what circumstances we disclose it.
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>